# Cursor Roles Configuration for EBWiki

## Environment Configuration Role
When setting up Ruby/RVM environment:
- Use ebwiki gemset only: `GEM_HOME="/usr/share/rvm/gems/ruby-3.4.2@ebwiki"`
- Exclude global gemset from GEM_PATH unless absolutely necessary
- Keep PATH minimal and avoid redundancy

## Testing Role
- Always verify tests pass before completing work
- Run full test suite: `bundle exec rspec spec/features/playwright`
- Verify server starts: `bundle exec rails server` (must start without errors)
- Never create documentation until tests confirm passing status

## Code Quality Role
- Fix deprecation warnings immediately
- Maintain version consistency across all version files
- Use proper RSpec conventions (type tags, matchers)
- Follow project branch naming: `feature/description` or `feature/EB-N-description`

## Browser Testing Role
- Playwright specs require WebMock localhost configuration
- Use flexible matchers for non-visible content
- Handle external service dependencies (Elasticsearch) gracefully

